%3Cli%3EAnysphere's%20CEO%20said%20programming%20without%20AI%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20time-boxed%20test%20for%20skill%20and%20intelligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECursor's%20hiring%20process%20ends%20with%20two-days%20at%20the%20office%2C%20where%20candidates%20build%20real%20projects%20with%20the%20team.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20hired%20at%20Cursor%2C%20an%20AI%20coding%20assistant%20built%20by%20Anysphere%2C%20you%20can't%20use%20AI%20in%20your%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20actually%20still%20interview%20people%20without%20allowing%20them%20to%20use%20AI%2C%20other%20than%20autocomplete%2C%20for%20first%20technical%20screens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20Truell%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Anysphere%2C%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20Y%20Combinator's%20podcast%20published%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProgramming%20without%20AI%20is%20still%20a%20really%20great%20time-boxed%20test%20for%20skill%20and%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20Truell%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20those%20are%20core%20qualities%20he%20looks%20for%20in%20a%20teammate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20reason%20behind%20the%20rule%3A%20fairness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20hired%20lots%20of%20people%20who%20are%20fantastic%20programmers%20who%20actually%20have%20no%20experience%20with%20AI%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20Truell%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20much%20rather%20hire%20those%20people%20and%20then%20teach%20them%20on%20the%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20beginner's%20mindset%20can%20be%20a%20product%20advantage%2C%20offering%20fresh%20insights%20from%20first-time%20users%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20step%20of%20Cursor's%20hiring%20process%20isn't%20a%20traditional%20interview.%20Shortlisted%20candidates%20are%20invited%20to%20the%20company's%20office%20for%20two%20days.%20They%20work%20on%20a%20real%20project%20alongside%20the%20team%2C%20join%20in%20for%20meals%2C%20and%20demo%20what%20they've%20built%20at%