h%20you%20don't%20see%20with%20most%20colleges.%20He's%20been%20able%20to%20support%20himself%20on%20his%20own%20since%20he%20graduated%20%E2%80%94%20this%20really%20is%20an%20industry%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20take%20care%20of%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e392bb1-43c0-4e9f-9182-10a9acb1807c%5C%22%3EThe%20opportunities%20for%20BMETs%20are%20vast%20%E2%80%94%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20awareness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20in%20the%20healthcare%20technology%20management%20industry%2C%20it%20was%20a%20little%20more%20challenging%20to%20find%20jobs.%20Today%2C%20the%20sky's%20the%20limit.%20There's%20a%20demand%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20industry%20and%20so%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-return-to-office-remote-work-raises-promotions-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopportunity%20for%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20can%20work%20in%20hospitals%2C%20for%20medical%20equipment%20manufacturers%2C%20on%20cruise%20ships%2C%20or%20as%20a%20traveling%20tech.%20You%20can%20be%20steady%20and%20stay%20put%2C%20or%20be%20adventurous%20and%20work%20across%20the%20country%20in%20a%20traveling%20biomedical%20equipment%20technician%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20get%20started%20with%20a%20certificate%2C%20an%20associate%20degree%2C%20or%20a%20bachelor's%20degree.%20There%20are%20even%20apprentice%20programs%20where%20you%20can%20get%20on-the-job%20training%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20of%20technicians%20are%20coming%20into%20the%20industry%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20that%20most%20people%20don't%20know%20about%20this%20industry.%20A%20lot%20of%20older%20BMETs%20are%20retiring%2C%20and%20not%20enough%20new%20people%20are%20entering%20to%20fill%20the%20gap.%20That's%20why%20I'm%20passionate%20about%20bringing%20awareness%20to%20this%20industry%2C%20which%20I%20do%20through%20speaking%20engagements%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fww