%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-trends-fueling-great-careers-include-infrastructure-experiential-and-artificial-intelligence-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrends%20to%20Bet%20Your%20Career%20On%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20about%20trending%20professional%20opportunities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHealthcare%20technology%20management%2C%20or%20HTM%2C%20is%20a%20growing%20field%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-paying-occupations-job-growth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epromising%20career%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20one%20that%20remains%20under%20the%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20ranked%2022nd%20in%20the%20US%20News%20%26amp%3B%20World%20Report's%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.usnews.com%2Fcareers%2Fbest-jobs%2Fmedical-equipment-repairer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20100%20best%20jobs%20of%202025%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%C2%A0US%C2%A0Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%2C%20jobs%20in%20medical%20equipment%20repair%20are%20expected%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fooh%2FInstallation-Maintenance-and-Repair%2FMedical-equipment-repairers.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20by%2018%25%20between%202023%20and%202033%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20a%20faster%20rate%20than%20average%20for%20all%20occupations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20are%20driving%20this%20growth.%20Medical%20equipment%20repairers%20or%20biomedical%20equipment%20technicians%20are%20an%20increasingly%20vital%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-hot-jobs-tech-layoffs-healthcare-government-careers-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20healthcare%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20maintain%2C%20calibrate%2C%20and%20repair%20everything%20from%20vital-sign%20monitors%20to%20MRIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20deliver%20healthcare%20without%20either%20a%20patient%2C%20a%20provider%2C%20or%20an%20instrument%2C%26quot%3B%20Jinesh%20Patel%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20medical%20equipment%20management%20company%20UptimeHealth%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20an%20X-ray%2C%20the%20radiologist%20isn't%20doing%20anything.%20Without%20a%20vitals%20monitor%2C%20the%20nurse%20can't%20tell%20you%20what's%20going%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-delays-work-marriage-children-homebuying-delayed-development-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindustry%20is%20also%20aging%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20faster%20than%20new%20BMETs%20can%20be%20trained.%20A%20survey%20from%20the%20Association%20for%20the%20Advancement%20of%20Medical%20Instrumentation%20found%20that%20about%20a%20third%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aami.org%2Fdocs%2Fdefault-source%2Fhtmdocs%2F2022-htm-retention-survey-results%2Fhtm-retention-survey-2022-053122.pdf%3Fsfvrsn%3D387eb9e0_2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHTM%20professionals%20are%20over%2055%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20large%20portion%20of%20our%20experienced%20workforce%20is%20reaching%20retirement%20age%2C%20leaving%20a%20significant%20talent%20gap%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kristi%20McDermott%2C%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20clinical%20asset%20management%20company%20Trimedx.%20She%20added%20that%20too%20few%20people%20know%20about%20the%20viability%2C%20or%20even%20existence%2C%20of%20this%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20vacuum%20of%20knowledge%20very%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patel%2C%20who%20added%20that%20he%20regularly%20struggles%20to%20find%20enough%20technicians%20for%20his%20hiring%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20projects%207%2C300