20the%20president%20of%20the%20College%20of%20Biomedical%20Equipment%20Technology%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20jobs%20require%20even%20less%20prior%20education%20and%20training%2C%20as%20some%20employers%20offer%20paid%20apprenticeships%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-training-broken-gen-z-mentorship-companies-employees-managers-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon-the-job%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20meet%20skyrocketing%20demand.%20Gonzales%20said%20that%20his%20college%20is%20constantly%20working%20with%20top-tier%20healthcare%20organizations%20to%20help%20technicians%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffind-job-searching-hunt-tips-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eland%20jobs%20faster%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20organizations%20all%20want%20the%20same%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20to%20reduce%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20establish%20minimum%20competency%20for%20an%20entry-level%20technician%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20willing%20to%20put%20in%20the%20sweat%20equity%20to%20support%20that%20individual's%20career%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20BMETs%20are%20also%20inspired%20by%20the%20ability%20to%20have%20a%20real-world%20impact%20on%20people's%20lives.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20actually%20helping%20create%20access%20to%20healthcare.%20Every%20time%20you%20get%20a%20machine%20back%20up%20and%20running%2C%20a%20patient%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20that%20machine%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20interested%20in%20pursuing%20a%20career%20that%20has%20real%20meaning%2C%20just%20look%20at%20the%20patient%20connected%20to%20the%20device%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20making%20a%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20Gonzales%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20sees%20a%20lot%20of%20veterans%2C%20like%20himself%2C%20pursue%20this%20as%20a%20second%20career%20for%20just%20that%20reason%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20served%20your