norance%20colours%20most%20opinions%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20thalassemia.%20Parents%20believe%20that%20their%20child%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20just%20get%20okay%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20take%20them%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3E(godman)%2C%20hoping%20to%20find%20a%20cure%2C%E2%80%9D%20Agarwal%20adds.%20But%20in%20his%20tenure%20as%20president%2C%20he%20has%20found%20a%20way%20around%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fthalassemia--1749549115.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Thalassemia%20and%20Sickle%20Cell%20Society%20(TSCS)%20is%20a%20registered%20NGO%20established%20in%20the%20year%201998%20with%20the%20pledge%20to%20help%20thalassemia%20patients%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fthalassemia--1749549115.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fthalassemia--1749549115-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fthalassemia--1749549115-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fthalassemia--1749549115-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fthalassemia--1749549115-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-447117%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThalassemia%20and%20Sickle%20Cell%20Society%20(TSCS)%20is%20a%20registered%20NGO%20established%20in%20the%20year%201998%20with%20the%20pledge%20to%20help%20thalassemia%20patients%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tscsindia.org%2Fwho-we-are%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETSCS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeeing%20is%20believing.%20So%20we%20put%20these%20parents%20in%20touch%20with%20other%20parents%20whose%20children%20have%20been%20battling%20thalassemia%20and%20who%20can%20vouch%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F413803%2Fgoa-blood-samaritan-mario-fernandes-100-donations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20transfusion%20helps%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20A%20conversation%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20a%20better%20understanding.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20parent%20sees%20their%20child%20feel%20better%20after%20a%20blood%20transfusion%2C%20they%20begin%20to%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20the%20right%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Agarwal%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20area%20where%20misunderstanding%20is%20rampant%20is%20the%20chelation%20therapy.%20A%20corollary%20of%20successive%20blood%20transfusions%20is%20the%20build-up%20of%20iron%20in%20the%20body.%20The%20excess%20iron%20needs%20to%20be%20removed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20chelation%2C%20Dr%20Suman%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20absolutely%20important%20for%20the%20iron%20that%20is%20coming%20along%20with%20the%20blood%20being%20transfused%20to%20be%20removed.%20The%20serum%20ferritin%20needs%20to%20be%20less%20than%201000%20ng%2FmL%2C%20but%20nearly%2020-25%20percent%20of%20our%20patients%E2%80%99%20parents%20do%20not%20understand%20this.%20One%20round%20of%20counselling%20is%20not%20enough%2C%20and%20so%20we%20repeatedly%20tell%20them%20to%20get%20the%20iron%20chelation%20done.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20chelate%20the%20iron.%20One%20is%20oral%20methods%20%E2%80%94%20tablets%20ingested%20%E2%80%94%20or%20subcutaneous%20injections.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20advise%20oral%20drugs%2C%20only%20if%20the%20iron%20levels%20are%20not%20being%20controlled%2C%20we%20start%20the%20child%20on%20injectables.%20The%20half-life%20of%20the%20drug%20in%20an%20injectable%20is%20short%2C%20and%20so%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20in%20the%20body%20for%20at%20least%2010%20hours.%20We%20monitor%20the%20serum%20iron%20levels%20every%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Suman%20adds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20food%20restrictions%2C%20she%20does%20not%20advise%20her%20patients%20on%20any%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F208525%2Fblood-donation-tips-precautions-health-myths-busted-by-doctor-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edietary%20modifications%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20tell%20them%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20meats%20and%20foods%20rich%20in%20iron.%20But%20considering%20that%20the%20major%20reason%20for%20iron%20build-up%20is%20the%20blood%20transfusion%20%E2%80%94%20every%20transfusion%20introduces%20200%20mg%20of%20iron%20in%20the%20body%20%E2%80%94%20diet%20does%20not%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EScreening%20%26amp%3B%20testing%3A%20A%20way%20to%20future-proof%20India%20against%20thalassemia%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20kinds%20of%20thalassemias%3A%20thalassemia%20major%2C%20thalassemia%20intermedia%2C%20and%20thalassemia%20minor.%20People%20born%20with%20thalassemia%20major%20and%20the%20severe%20form%20of%20thalassemia%20intermedia%20require%20lifelong%20blood%20transfusions%20and%20iron%20ch