tterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FScreenshot-2025-06-10-151417-1749548688.jpg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FScreenshot-2025-06-10-151417-1749548688-300x239.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FScreenshot-2025-06-10-151417-1749548688-500x399.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FScreenshot-2025-06-10-151417-1749548688-150x120.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-447111%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22574%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20genetic%20transmission%20of%20thalassemia%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsickle.nhm.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fguidelines%2FNHM_Guidelines_on_Hemoglobinopathies_in_India.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Health%20Mission%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Health%20Mission%20recommends%20carrier%20screening%2C%20genetic%20counselling%2C%20and%20prenatal%20diagnosis%20as%20a%20preventative%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20TSCS%2C%20led%20by%20Agarwal%2C%20steps%20in.%20A%202022%20study%20by%20Genome%20Foundation%20and%20the%20Thalassemia%20and%20Sickle%20Cell%20Society%20(TSCS)%20found%20that%20four%20districts%20in%20Telangana%20were%20driving%20the%20average%20for%20high%20risk%20of%20Beta-Thalassemia.%20One%20of%20these%20was%20Mahabubnagar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWould%20you%20believe%20that%20today%2C%20Mahbubnagar%20is%20leading%20the%20way%20in%20thalassemia%20control%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgarwal%20explains%20how%2C%20following%20an%20MoU%20signed%20with%20the%20Collector%20of%20Mahbubnagar%20in%202022%2C%20100%20percent%20pre-natal%20screening%20was%20done.%20This%20means%20that%20every%20year%2C%20since%202022%2C%20every%20pregnant%20woman%20in%20Mahabubnagar%20has%20been%20screened%20%E2%80%94%20Agarwal%20credits%20the%20ASHA%20workers%20for%20this%20assistance%20%E2%80%94%20to%20check%20for%20thalassemia%20carriers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20pregnant%20mother%20is%20found%20to%20be%20a%20carrier%20of%20the%20thalassemia%20gene%2C%20the%20father%20is%20tested.%20If%20he%20too%20is%20found%20to%20be%20a%20carrier%2C%20the%20foetus%20is%20tested%2C%20and%20if%20found%20to%20be%20thalassemia%20major%2C%20the%20next%20step%20is%20counselling.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20counsel%20the%20to-be%20parents%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F208322%2Fbengaluru-teen-teacher-death-blood-donation-community-inspiring-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lifetime%20of%20blood%20transfusions%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20child%20will%20have%20to%20have%2C%20the%20difficulties%20of%20growing%20up%20with%20thalassemia%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20Agarwal%20explains.%20The%20focus%20is%20on%20giving%20parents%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20make%20an%20informed%20decision%20about%20whether%20to%20carry%20on%20with%20the%20pregnancy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20district%20collector%20of%20Mahbubnagar%20(wishing%20to%20remain%20anonymous)%20has%20commended%20the%20%E2%80%9Cextraordinary%20impact%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20project.%20Now%2C%20TSCS%20is%20looking%20to%20clone%20the%20model%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20districts%20with%20government%20approval.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesting%20is%20a%20pragmatic%20necessity%2C%20Agarwal%20shares%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20expectant%20parents%20who%20must%20be%20screened%2C%20but%20also%20families%20where%20there%20is%20a%20thalassemia%20major%20person.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20case%20of%20a%20person%20with%20thalassemia%20major%2C%20we%20screened%2078%20family%20members%20of%20theirs%2C%20and%2027%20percent%20were%20found%20to%20be%20thalassemia%20minors.%E2%80%9D%20Early%20screening%20means%20early%20detection%2C%20which%20can%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20early%20counselling%20and%20thus%20a%20preventative%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20well%20be%20the%20contingency%20plan%20India%20needs%20to%20curb%20its%20thalassemia%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20until%20then%2C%20your%20blood%20donation%20could%20save%20a%20child%20struggling%20with%20thalassemia.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20World%20Blood%20Donor%20Day%2C%20if%20you%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20step%20in%20and%20help%20a%20child%2C%20check%20out%20the%20various%20camps%20TSCS%20is%20having%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tscsindia.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetailm.aspx%3FPRID%3D1841433%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVice%20President%20calls%20for%20focus%20on%20preventive%20measures%20to%20address%20the%20huge%20burden%20of%20genetic%20diseases%20in%20the%20country%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%2C%20Published%20on%2014%20July%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftelangana%2F2022%2FJan%2F27%2Ffour-districts-in-ts-at-high-risk-of-thalassemia-says-study-2411783.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFour%20districts%20in%20TS%20at%20high%20risk%20of%20Thalassemia%2C%20says%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20The%20New%20Indian%20Express%2C%20Published%20on%2027%20January%202022.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-he