0by%20her%20father-in-law%20and%20her%20uncle%2C%20now%20employs%20over%2035%20women%20from%20nearby%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20clear.%20The%20women%20in%20our%20villages%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20leave%20home%20for%20jobs.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20create%20employment%20right%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20She%20now%20mentors%20other%20women%20to%20become%20financially%20independent.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tell%20them%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20time.%20Make%20time.%20Even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20one%20hour%20a%20day%2C%20use%20it%20to%20work%20on%20your%20dream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStaying%20grounded%2C%20dreaming%20bigger%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20fame%20and%20success%2C%20Kaushalya%20remains%20grounded.%20%E2%80%9CI%20still%20want%20to%20be%20the%20same%20daughter-in-law%2C%20mother%2C%20and%20sister%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been.%20I%20just%20want%20more%20women%20to%20realise%20their%20worth%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20goal%20now%3F%20To%20help%20thousands%20of%20Kaushalyas%20rise%20from%20small%20villages%2C%20not%20just%20to%20seek%20jobs%2C%20but%20to%20build%20empires%20of%20their%20own.%20She%E2%80%99s%20working%20on%20a%20platform%20to%20help%20rural%20women%20start%20micro-businesses%20through%20the%20Sidhi%20Marwari%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20message%20to%20women%20is%20simple%20but%20powerful%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20decide%20you%20want%20to%20do%20something%2C%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20follow%20Kaushalya%E2%80%99s%20journey%20and%20explore%20her%20food%20products%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWebsite%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsidhimarwadi.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esidhimarwadi.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20YouTube%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A