0%20for%20the%20setup.%20I%20admire%20Dinil%20for%20his%20dedication.%20He%20spent%20so%20many%20years%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20his%20decision%20to%20switch%20careers%20is%20commendable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECage%20fish%20farming%3A%20An%20overview%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDinil%20explains%20that%20caged%20fish%20farming%20is%20a%20method%20of%20cultivating%20fish%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment.%20This%20involves%20placing%20fish%20in%20cages%20or%20enclosures%20that%20are%20submerged%20in%20natural%20water%20bodies%20such%20as%20rivers%2C%20lakes%2C%20or%20seas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cages%20allow%20water%20to%20flow%20freely%20through%20them%2C%20providing%20a%20steady%20supply%20of%20oxygen%20and%20nutrients%20to%20the%20fish%20while%20containing%20them%20within%20a%20defined%20area.%20This%20farming%20system%20mimics%20fish%E2%80%99s%20natural%20habitat%20but%20allows%20for%20greater%20control%20over%20the%20environment%20and%20protection%20from%20predators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdinil-prasad-cage-fish-farming-4-1749217532.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caged%20fish%20farming%2C%20Dinil%20explains%2C%20is%20a%20method%20of%20cultivating%20fish%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdinil-prasad-cage-fish-farming-4-1749217532.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdinil-prasad-cage-fish-farming-4-1749217532-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdinil-prasad-cage-fish-farming-4-1749217532-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F202