0comfort%2C%20and%20it%20is%20something%20that%20I%20resonate%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20personally.%20And%20Ali%20is%20the%20yellow%20seed.%20It%20translates%20to%20the%20seed%20of%20comfort%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dimum.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20name%20that%20beautifully%20captures%20her%20vision%20%E2%80%94%20offering%20not%20just%20food%20but%20a%20sense%20of%20nourishment%2C%20security%2C%20and%20well-being%20through%20this%20revived%20grain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20so%20special%20about%20adlay%20millet%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20adlay%20millet%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20special%20because%20it%20was%20a%20lost%20crop%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20special%20because%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fthey-call-me-queen-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20its%20nutritional%20value.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CLike%20most%20millets%2C%20adlay%20also%20has%20a%20very%20low%20glycemic%20index%20(GI)%2C%20making%20it%20a%20good%20alternative%20grain%20l%20for%20people%20with%20diabetes%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dimum.%20With%20the%20richness%20of%20fibre%2C%20it%20can%20be%20your%20gut%E2%80%99s%20friend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDimum%20was%20quick%20to%20recognise%20adlay%E2%80%99s%20potential%20as%20a%20healthy%20alternative.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20selling%20it%20as%20a%20grain%2C%20I%20noticed%20quinoa%20was%20its%20closest%20competitor.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20exactly%20like%20rice%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20cooked%20in%20a%20similar%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20makes%20adlay%20a%20worthy%20competitor%20with%20quinoa%20is