ipating%20in%20startup%20competitions%20and%20expos.%20I%20was%20happy%20when%20I%20knew%20that%20Gepo%20Aali%20will%20be%20representing%20India%20%E2%80%94%20Adlay%20millets%20to%20be%20specific%2C%20among%20global%20competitors%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dimum%2C%20a%20significant%20milestone%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22people%20visiting%20the%20farm%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-445479%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20international%20recognition%20pushed%20Dimum%20to%20focus%20more%20reviving%20such%20lost%20millets%20and%20vegetables.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20took%20some%20of%20my%20products%20there%20and%20it%20was%20quite%20interesting%20to%20across%20people%20from%20different%20ethnicities%20coming%20together%20with%20different%20ideas%20It%20was%20a%20big%20exposure%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20her%20surprise%2C%20people%20were%20genuinely%20curious%20about%20her%20millet.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20carried%20two%20packets%20of%20the%20millet%20and%20they%20bought%20both%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20Dimum%20is%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20fellow%20delegate%20from%20the%20expo%20who%20is%20interested%20in%20procuring%20more%20of%20the%20revived%20millet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20joy%20of%20reviving%20lost%20foods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20two%20years%2C%20Gepo%20Aali%20has%20garnered%20around%20150%20loyal%20customers%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%94%20a%20small%20but%20meaningful%20community%20that%20believes%20in%20Dimum%E2%80%99s%20vision.%20While%20revenue%20has%20been%20modest%2C%20reflecting%20the%20challenges%20of%20scaling%20a%20grassroots%20food%20venture%20in%20a%20remote%20region%2C%20Dimum%20remains%20undeterred.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20focus%20has%20never%20been%20on%20rapid%20growth%20or%20profit%20margins.%20Instead%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20rooted%20in%20steady%20and%20sustainable%20impact%20%E2%80%94%20building%20seed%20banks%2C%20empowering%20women%20through%20financial%20models%20like%20ROCA%20(Rotating%20Savings%20and%20Credit%20Association)%2C%20and%20preserving%20indigenous%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20her%20goals%20are%20ambitious%20yet%20deeply%20connected%20with%20community%20care.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20look%20for%20more%20such%20foods%20and%20revive%20them%20effectively%2C%20bring%20them%20to%20our%20seed%20bank%2C%20and%20expand%20our%20women%20workforce.%20%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20aim%20is%20not%20just%20agricultural%20revival%2C%20but%20financial%20inclusion%20%E2%80%94%20giving%20women%20the%20tools%20and%20support%20to%20grow%2C%20earn%2C%20and%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20of%20course%2C%20she%20dreams%20of%20sending%20the%20goodness%20of%20Adlay%20millet%20across%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20year