n%20our%20environment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20hidden%20threat%20in%20your%20medicine%20cabinet%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20producers%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332843%2Fdr-pal-palaniappan-manickam-medical-comedy-show-weight-loss-intermittent-fasting-health-tips-standup-comedian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumers%20of%20pharmaceuticals%3C%2Fa%3E%20globally.%20According%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%2C%20India%20generates%20approximately%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenterclimate.com%2Fbio-medical-waste-authorization%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAuthorisation%2520Requirements%2520of%2520Common%2520Biomedical%2Cas%2520per%2520the%2520SPCB%2FPCC.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20484%20tonnes%20of%20biomedical%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20per%20day%2C%20a%20significant%20chunk%20of%20which%20includes%20unused%20and%20expired%20medicines%20from%20homes%2C%20clinics%20and%20pharmacies.%20Unfortunately%2C%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20nationwide%20system%20for%20collecting%20and%20safely%20disposing%20of%20household%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%5C%22%